View Member's: Reviews I ordered a Hotpoint wt960p washing machine from Whitebox on the Thursday and it was here on the following Monday. Whitebox called, as per their website, within two hours of placing the order, to confirm delivery would be on the Monday between 7am and 1pm. Hotpoint called 30 minutes later to confirm this.
